Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.71,0:00:06.81,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.07,0:00:15.30,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.50,0:00:27.60,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.44,0:00:33.69,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The leader of the Eye of \Nthe Midnight Sun, Licht.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.69,0:00:38.16,italics,naR,0000,0000,0000,,Asta was no match for his \Noverwhelming magical powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.20,0:00:40.95,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The one who came to Asta's rescue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.95,0:00:44.35,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,was none other than the captain \Nof the Black Bulls, Yami Sukehiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.46,0:00:49.58,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,In a breathless battle between \Nlight magic and dark magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.58,0:00:53.50,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Asta went beyond his limits and \Nclosed in for his counterattack.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.50,0:00:54.67,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.67,0:00:58.47,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you... harm Valtos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.85,0:01:03.18,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot allow people like \Nyou to harm my comrades
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.58,0:01:05.56,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.56,0:01:09.27,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Light Creation Magic: Light Whip of Judgment!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.86,0:01:15.78,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless to struggle!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.37,0:01:19.45,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The cave!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.91,0:01:24.08,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,That nutcase has gone ballistic!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.23,0:01:37.13,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear... I held back most of my magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.13,0:01:39.47,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,but it's all really too fragile...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.02,0:01:42.80,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Both this world and you fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.80,0:01:47.77,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, Master Licht!\NYour strength is practically divine!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.77,0:01:52.44,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,If you felt like it, Master Licht, the Magic \NKnights would be no more than infants!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.44,0:01:55.59,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.33,0:02:13.96,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,The Light of Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.59,0:03:36.75,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,If you concentrate like that, you can \Nsense the ki of natural objects, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.75,0:03:39.71,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,That way, you'll never get killed\Nby stuff like falling rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.98,0:03:44.77,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ki is awesome! Hooray for ki!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.77,0:03:46.22,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ki is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.77,0:03:46.22,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.15,0:03:48.76,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.76,0:03:52.56,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Now take it up a notch and go after the \Nwhite-haired dude with the round eyebrows!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.56,0:03:53.90,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.90,0:03:56.85,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I think I could do that right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.85,0:04:01.48,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Because of my ki,\NI'm enthusiastic, energetic, and confident!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.48,0:04:03.76,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hope you're ready, Round Brows!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.67,0:04:06.39,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, scratch that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:07.37,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.75,0:04:11.58,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I told him that I'd show him the \Npower of a captain, so I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.58,0:04:13.22,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, if you did it, you'd die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.22,0:04:17.98,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But then what am I supposed to \Ndo with all this extra energy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.98,0:04:18.88,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Not my problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:22.63,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You can tackle that scrawny line-faced dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.27,0:04:25.68,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.68,0:04:28.93,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while since I've let loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:23.94,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Magic:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:26.03,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Cloaked
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.03,0:05:27.96,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Lightless Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.03,0:05:30.45,italics,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.01,0:05:33.70,italics,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,My magic is being drawn in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:37.08,italics,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the power of dark magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.41,0:05:38.33,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.91,0:05:43.09,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I know that, it'll be \Nimpossible for you to get me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.49,0:05:47.42,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you were in the middle \Nof some weird story,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.42,0:05:49.80,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,but that wasn't the end of it, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.23,0:05:54.65,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,That grimoire means you're a citizen \Nof the Clover Kingdom, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.65,0:05:56.65,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Why attack your own country?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.79,0:06:19.12,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,You're wide open.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.26,0:06:25.92,italics,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,He left himself wide open \Nso I'd let my guard down...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.92,0:06:28.63,italics,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Yami Sukehiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.63,0:06:30.47,italics,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,You are a worthy foe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.20,0:06:41.02,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me. What's your real goal here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.07,0:06:47.73,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're a foreigner, I'm sure \Nyou've noticed them, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.79,0:06:50.79,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,The distortions in this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:54.54,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Some are on the brink of \Ndeath from starvation,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.54,0:06:57.05,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,but others have so much excess \Nfood that they throw it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.08,0:07:01.14,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,People are ranked by how much \Nor how little magic they have,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.83,0:07:06.32,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,but some have great magic, yet are \Ndiscriminated against for reasons of birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.83,0:07:11.57,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Some are hurt in the name of justice \Nbecause they were born in another country.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.82,0:07:16.80,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,We were born from these distortions...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.14,0:07:19.56,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,In order to correct them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.56,0:07:22.47,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not seeing the point here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.47,0:07:26.86,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you trying to do the same \Nthing these distorted people do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.86,0:07:29.86,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sane?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:32.34,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Perfectly sane.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:35.11,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Let me answer your sins with sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.11,0:07:38.16,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,So you're gonna have it \Nyour way, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.16,0:07:40.62,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I like guys like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.03,0:07:42.00,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.71,0:07:45.04,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I hate your guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.78,0:08:19.23,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's with this battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.28,0:08:22.66,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the captain's
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.66,0:08:24.09,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,full power...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:29.75,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any magic. Can I \Nsurpass them, even if I train?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.96,0:08:35.20,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This guy, Yuno, and the Wizard King...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.80,0:08:44.31,italics,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,To think that he has enough power to \Ngo head to head with Master Licht...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.43,0:08:48.06,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,Master Licht! Please allow me to assist you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.65,0:08:53.19,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.53,0:08:55.90,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.32,0:08:58.74,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you wimping out, you dumbass?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.10,0:09:01.74,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I left that scrawny guy to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.22,0:09:04.45,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I don't give guys jobs they can't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.47,0:09:08.46,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Do something about him in your own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.87,0:09:13.88,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.69,0:09:18.68,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... I'm going to become \Nthe Wizard King, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.68,0:09:21.41,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to get depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.93,0:09:24.58,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.58,0:09:28.69,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,First, I'll become the guy who beats you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.03,0:09:30.31,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get me twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.12,0:09:34.82,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,Spatial Magic: Myriad Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.23,0:09:40.47,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,You may be able to see what's coming, \Nbut can you block all of these?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.35,0:09:55.50,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,One of them got through...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.50,0:09:58.01,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,This will go on forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.01,0:10:01.01,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,Until you can't move anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.37,0:10:14.48,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,You dared defy Master Licht \Ndespite having no magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.48,0:10:16.38,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,You will pay with your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.36,0:10:25.37,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it... I don't think I'm going \Nto last until he runs out of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.26,0:10:30.22,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I manage to repel his attacks, \Nat this rate, he's going to beat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.22,0:10:34.42,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down and think... Do this my own way...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.80,0:10:40.76,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,You threw away your only weapons?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.12,0:10:43.01,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,Have you lost your mind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.65,0:10:48.02,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll take you \Nout with an extra-big one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.32,0:11:05.78,italics,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,He jumped into my space?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.67,0:11:24.95,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You just punched him in the face!\NYou're hilarious, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.05,0:11:27.19,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,You let your guard down again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.21,0:11:29.99,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.23,0:11:33.31,italics,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,My attack was absorbed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.59,0:11:37.40,italics,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,And I can't move...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.03,0:11:41.40,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Magic: Black Hole, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.40,0:11:44.90,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Magic: Dark Cloaked
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.57,0:11:47.03,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Black Blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.43,0:12:06.22,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Yami!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.37,0:12:09.47,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.82,0:12:11.22,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,You got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.62,0:12:16.11,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably within five meters. \NThe range is definitely limited,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.11,0:12:18.11,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,but to think there was a magic
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.11,0:12:20.58,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,that could absorb my own magic \Nand stop me from moving...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.73,0:12:24.80,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Dark magic is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.80,0:12:29.78,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,The one attribute that's the \Nnatural enemy of my light magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.74,0:12:34.80,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,However, dark magic is extremely slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.80,0:12:38.77,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Light has absolute speed, making them\Npolar opposites there, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.22,0:12:42.88,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you cloaked \Nyour weapon in darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.88,0:12:46.26,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,and created a combat style that uses \Nreinforcement magic to compensate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.33,0:12:52.13,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.13,0:12:54.27,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Why does it sound like he's bragging?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.27,0:12:58.85,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what's up? You can \Nuse recovery magic, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.85,0:13:00.77,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,So hurry up and heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:04.47,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,But while you're healing yourself, \NI'm going to get real close
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.47,0:13:06.45,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,and chop you up even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.83,0:13:12.49,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,I'll admit it. You're the second person \NI've met with the power to defeat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.82,0:13:17.25,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,But I sadly cannot waste my time with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.58,0:13:19.72,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What was that, punk?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.72,0:13:21.46,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,And whaddaya mean, the second?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.83,0:13:27.16,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,I still have an ultimate enemy left who \Ninflicted this unhealable wound on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.16,0:13:32.21,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,the Wizard King, Julius Novachrono.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.72,0:13:37.39,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,This is currently my greatest magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.99,0:13:40.51,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Speed you cannot avoid...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.51,0:13:43.82,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,A spell with such a wide range and \Nhigh output that pulling it in
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.82,0:13:46.80,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,with that spell you used won't do any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.36,0:13:53.45,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,You will meet your end the moment I \Nrelease this, Captain of the Black Bulls.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.45,0:13:55.57,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell he will!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.57,0:13:58.25,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Quit underestimating Captain Yami!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.25,0:14:00.17,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Your face is stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.17,0:14:03.67,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's not good. \NThat's some insane magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.67,0:14:05.46,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.81,0:14:13.22,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Boy. You will also be punished for\Nhurting Valtos, and return that grimoire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.22,0:14:18.48,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,That's definitely a four-leaf for you... \NHis magical abilities are off the charts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.48,0:14:22.17,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Unless I catch him by surprise, \Nhe'll just dodge any slash at light speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.17,0:14:23.23,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:28.16,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave that up to the me \Nof five seconds from now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.70,0:14:30.99,main,Kid a,0000,0000,0000,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.73,0:14:32.95,main,Kid b,0000,0000,0000,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.31,0:14:34.89,main,Kid A,0000,0000,0000,,I was so scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.89,0:14:35.91,main,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,There, there...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.91,0:14:37.70,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.76,0:14:41.71,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,That should be everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.12,0:14:44.88,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare die, you old hag!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.23,0:14:47.09,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wake up, old hag!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.09,0:14:49.82,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You're supposed to be some \Nimmortal monster hag!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.82,0:14:51.51,main,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.91,0:14:55.89,main,Marco,0000,0000,0000,,N-No... Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.39,0:15:03.65,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Gauche, you're hurt really badly, too, \Nso you should worry about your own—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.65,0:15:04.86,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.86,0:15:08.00,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... I'm the one with\Nseniority here, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.83,0:15:14.66,main,Mage 1,0000,0000,0000,,Gauche's treatments will be done soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.66,0:15:15.64,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.64,0:15:21.37,main,Mage 1,0000,0000,0000,,Well, all of his wounds just \Nbarely missed his vital points.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.68,0:15:23.63,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,So he was lucky?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.63,0:15:25.38,main,Mage 1,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure. That just seems...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:28.66,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Then hurry up and treat the old hag, not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.66,0:15:30.17,main,Mage 1,0000,0000,0000,,O-Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.17,0:15:34.35,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Old hag! Wake up already! Old hag—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.12,0:15:35.23,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Tone it down...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.53,0:15:40.10,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear you, idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.10,0:15:41.60,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Old hag!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.97,0:15:43.23,main,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.23,0:15:51.11,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Take my magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.35,0:15:54.80,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to save them, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.47,0:15:57.99,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta and the others...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.63,0:16:00.74,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I never said I'd...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.09,0:16:06.13,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,You changed... after meeting him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.00,0:16:10.10,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, Gauche.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.57,0:16:12.48,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Old hag!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.39,0:16:19.97,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You're joking, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.65,0:16:23.27,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You said you could die?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.87,0:16:25.33,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Bring her back to life!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.33,0:16:26.30,main,Mage 1,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.30,0:16:27.24,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.24,0:16:28.44,main,Mage 1,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.44,0:16:29.94,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Marie's going to be sad, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.25,0:16:31.52,main,Mage 1,0000,0000,0000,,She's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.44,0:16:33.94,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.94,0:16:35.36,main,Mage 1,0000,0000,0000,,She's not dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.22,0:16:39.95,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You old hag! Stop being so misleading!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.37,0:16:43.38,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a monster hag, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.79,0:16:47.71,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,I won't kick the bucket so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.10,0:16:52.53,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Relax and get over there, \Nyou sister complex freak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.35,0:16:56.45,main,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,Take my magic, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.45,0:16:57.62,main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Mine, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.62,0:16:58.78,main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Mine, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.78,0:17:00.72,main,Marco,0000,0000,0000,,Please save Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.22,0:17:05.31,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,Please use my magic, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.31,0:17:06.62,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.62,0:17:11.48,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very sorry for being \Nviolent toward your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.79,0:17:22.47,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be of any help if I went.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.47,0:17:25.50,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,Please take care of Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.50,0:17:27.04,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.75,0:17:34.25,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,See? Everyone lives by supporting each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.69,0:17:35.68,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Marie...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.68,0:17:41.28,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You just protect what you want to protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.85,0:17:45.06,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, that'll help somebody out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.68,0:17:50.72,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I know what I have to do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.72,0:17:52.63,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Finral!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.63,0:17:53.56,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Erk...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.56,0:17:55.69,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Take me back to that cave!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.69,0:17:57.74,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,S-Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.74,0:17:59.95,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm your senior, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.32,0:18:02.71,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, even if we go back,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.71,0:18:05.51,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,are you going to be able to do anything \Nabout that blinding magic guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.51,0:18:07.45,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't stand a chance earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.45,0:18:09.46,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,so it's probably better to\Nwait for reinforcements.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.31,0:18:12.29,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I thought of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.29,0:18:13.29,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.29,0:18:16.30,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Unless I'm wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.30,0:18:18.39,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,We've got a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.39,0:18:21.43,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,We won't be able to surprise \Nattack him with my spatial magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.31,0:18:26.35,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,People with powerful magic have force \Nfields of magic that appear around them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.35,0:18:28.34,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to get that close.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.98,0:18:33.48,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention, I moved way too \Nmany people really far today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.48,0:18:36.89,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I may only be able to use \Nmy magic one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.89,0:18:37.91,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.91,0:18:39.11,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.11,0:18:40.02,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Finral...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.54,0:18:42.50,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.67,0:18:49.01,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.58,0:18:51.44,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.47,0:18:54.08,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Magic:
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.73,0:18:56.02,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Black Cocoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.09,0:18:59.05,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.05,0:19:01.85,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I've gone into defensive mode, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.85,0:19:03.80,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,It's hopeless. He's gonna kill us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.80,0:19:06.91,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What?! How are you so calm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.91,0:19:10.41,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then! I'll just deflect it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.41,0:19:13.21,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Nah. The swords will probably \Nbe all that's left of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.21,0:19:14.94,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.26,0:19:17.43,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Then what should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.43,0:19:20.07,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Not give up until the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.07,0:19:21.95,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're just trying to act cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.68,0:19:29.95,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,To be completely honest,\Nthere's nothing we can do right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.66,0:19:33.96,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Grit your teeth and stand firm.\NThat's all we can do right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.21,0:19:40.96,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell, Yami Sukehiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.40,0:19:47.26,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, what the hell?! \NDid we come to the wrong place?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.64,0:19:48.85,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.85,0:19:50.97,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,That's Yami's magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.97,0:19:54.98,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Gah! This has gotten way out of hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.04,0:20:00.73,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Light Magic: Ray of Divine Punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.91,0:20:03.92,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,He came.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.22,0:20:07.34,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.99,0:20:11.37,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Mirror Magic: Full Reflection!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.51,0:20:28.76,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how big or strong it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.12,0:20:31.31,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Mirrors reflect light!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.66,0:20:57.42,main,Veto,0000,0000,0000,,To think someone could wound Sally this badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.99,0:21:01.00,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I hate them. This is unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.20,0:21:07.65,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,This is annoying, but it\Nlooks like it's our turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.02,0:22:48.49,sign_33083_276_Petit_Clover_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,520)}Pe{\c&H3BC020&}t{\c&HE2AF0F&}i{\c&H3BC020&}t C{\c&HE2AF0F&}l{\c&H3BC020&}o{\c&H0E42D4&}ve{\c&H3BC020&}r
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.96,0:22:47.92,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.34,0:22:51.99,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}Voice Change
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.07,0:22:50.40,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Voice Change.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.95,0:22:55.60,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,M-Marie's coughing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.60,0:22:57.26,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Did you catch a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.26,0:23:00.66,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,It was pretty cold in the cave! \NAre you all right, Marie?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.66,0:23:03.21,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, my throat's just a little sore.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.21,0:23:04.20,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.24,0:23:06.42,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,My voice sounds strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.41,0:23:11.63,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,M-My angel Marie's voice \Nsounds like Captain Yami's!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.63,0:23:15.80,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, Brother, \Ngo save Asta and the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.21,0:23:18.85,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Take my magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.18,0:23:20.87,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,The old hag's voice is weird, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.27,0:23:24.39,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I may only be able to use \Nmy magic one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.39,0:23:25.81,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You, too, Finral?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.39,0:23:30.03,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, now my throat is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.03,0:23:31.84,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Your voice is cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.70,0:23:38.41,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I did it, Marie! Your big \Nbrother defeated the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.41,0:23:41.50,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I need to hurry back to Marie... \NWho the hell are you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.50,0:23:43.71,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,No one said anything about reinforcements!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.71,0:23:46.75,main,gauche,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 36: "Three Eyes."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.71,0:23:50.39,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 36\N\N{\fs18} Three Eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.75,0:23:49.09,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I might not be able to \Ngo back just yet, Marie.
